quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  23,91,"Allāhu kò fi ẹnì kan kan ṣe ọmọ, kò sì sí ọlọ́hun kan pẹ̀lú Rẹ̀. (Tí kò bá rí bẹ́ẹ̀) nígbà náà, ọlọ́hun kọ̀ọ̀kan ìbá ti kó ẹ̀dá tó dá lọ, apá kan wọn ìbá sì borí apá kan. Mímọ́ ni fún Allāhu tayọ ohun tí wọ́n ń fi ròyìn (Rẹ̀ nípa ọmọ bíbí)."
  23,92,"(Allāhu) Onímọ̀-ìkọ̀kọ̀ àti gban̄gba. Nítorí náà, Ó ga tayọ n̄ǹkan tí wọ́n fi ń ṣẹbọ sí I."
  23,93,"Sọ pé: “Olúwa mi, Ó ṣeé ṣe kí Ó fi ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣèlérí rẹ̀ fún wọn hàn mí,"
  25,37,"(Rántí) ìjọ (Ànábì) Nūh. Nígbà tí wọ́n pe àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ ní òpùrọ́, A tẹ̀ wọ́n rì sínú omi. A sì ṣe wọ́n ní àmì kan fún àwọn ènìyàn. A sì ti pèsè ìyà ẹlẹ́ta-eléro sílẹ̀ de àwọn alábòsí."
  25,38,"(Rántí) àwọn ìjọ ‘Ād, ìjọ Thamūd, ìjọ Rass àti àwọn ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ ìran mìíràn (tó ń bẹ) láààrin wọn."
  25,39,"Ìkọ̀ọ̀kan wọn ni A fún ní àwọn àpẹ̀ẹrẹ (gẹ́gẹ́ bí ẹ̀rí àti àlàyé ọ̀rọ̀). Ìkọ̀ọ̀kan wọn sì ni A parun pátápátá (torí àìgbàgbọ́ wọn)."
  26,10,"(Rántí) nígbà tí Olúwa rẹ pe (Ànábì) Mūsā pé: “Lọ bá ìjọ alábòsí,"
  26,11,"ìjọ Fir‘aon (kí o sì sọ̱ fún wọn) pé, ‘Ṣé wọn kò níí bẹ̀rù (Allāhu) ni.’ ”"
  26,12,"Ó sọ pé: “Olúwa mi, dájúdájú èmi ń bẹ̀rù pé wọ́n máa pè mí ní òpùrọ́."